### 1. Correctness — Acceptance Criteria Verification

| Criterion | Status | Notes |
|-----------|--------|-------|
| Vocal filter partitions by threshold | ✅ PASS | `tests/unit/test_vocal_filter.py` correctly tests thresholds (0.0, 0.3) for instrumental and (0.6, 1.0) for vocal |
| PlaylistsView smoke test shows vocal chips | ✅ PASS | `TestVocalFilterControls` class verifies `_vocal_btn_any`, `_vocal_btn_instrumental`, `_vocal_btn_vocal` exist |
