**Implementation Summary:**

1. **SetBuilderView** (`playchitect/gui/views/set_builder_view.py`):
   - Timeline lane with `Gtk.Box(HORIZONTAL)` inside `Gtk.ScrolledWindow(HORIZONTAL)` 
   - `TrackCard(Gtk.Frame)` widgets showing: 2-char sequence number, truncated title, BPM, coloured energy mini-bar, and transition indicator dots (green/amber/red via `compatibility_score`)
   - Drag-and-drop reorder using `Gtk.DragSource` + `Gtk.DropTarget` with `GdkContentProvider`
   - Left browser panel with `Gtk.ColumnView` (Title, Artist, BPM) - double-click adds to timeline
   - Energy block filter chips
   - [Auto-fill] button calling `next_track_suggestions` greedily
   - [Export Set] button writing M3U via `M3UExporter`
   - Footer with total duration, mean BPM, mean rms_energy

2. **Tests** (`tests/gui/test_set_builder_view.py`):
   - 21 smoke tests covering all acceptance criteria
   - Tests for TrackCard, SetBuilderView, auto-fill, export button, footer labels

